('Grammar and Structure', 'Prefixes and Suffixes', 'advisory', 'The committee issued an advisory notice. What does \"-ory\" indicate?', 'Relating to', 'Without', 'Full of', 'Capable', '\"-ory\" means \"pertaining to\" (advise → advisory)'),
